version_description: This is the first 100% accurate version of this song in its entirety on this site.
This version contains the entire song, including the ending that every other version leaves off.
Acoustic performance at the Bridge School Benefit: https://youtu.be/njrtXea6Euk?t=521.
This tab uses an open G chord unlike the other tab. It also features the D/F# Chord and uses Cadd9 more.
